Creating Questionnaire Subscales

qdat_child <- dplyr::select(dat, age, social_secret:nao_hear)

qdat_means <- qdat_child %>%
  dplyr::mutate(
    social = rowMeans(select(., social_secret, social_honest, social_trust)),
    competency = rowMeans(select(., comp_knows, comp_smart, comp_reliable, comp_teacher)),
    liking = rowMeans(select(., like_likenao, like_naothem, like_comfort)),
    agency = rowMeans(select(., agency_feelings, agency_think, agency_move, agency_onoff))) %>%
  select(., social, competency, liking, agency)

dat <- cbind(dat, qdat_means)
